# ğŸ® Healthingshot

> **Aim the junk food for the love of life**

An interactive exergaming project created during MMI Night 2026, combining physical activity with gaming through innovative body movement detection.

## ğŸ“– About

Healthingshot is a 24-hour challenge project developed during the MMI Night 2026 (January 8-9, 2026). This exergaming experience encourages players to move their bodies to progress, promoting physical activity and combating sedentary behavior in a fun and engaging way.

### ğŸ¯ Key Features

- **Physical Interaction**: Perform squats to get ammunition (1 squat = 1 bullet)
- **Motion Tracking**: Aim using your hand in front of the webcam
- **Makey Makey Integration**: Shoot using modeling clay connected to Makey Makey
- **ML5.js Pose Detection**: Real-time body movement tracking with MoveNet
- **Progressive Levels**: Eliminate unhealthy food items to advance through levels
- **Health Awareness**: Lose a life if you hit healthy food items

## ğŸš€ Live Demo

- **Play the game**: [Healthingshot Game](https://florianmmi.github.io/HealthlingShot/Jeu/)
- **Landing Page**: [Project Website](https://florianmmi.github.io/HealthlingShot/)

## ğŸ› ï¸ Technologies Used

- **Frontend**: HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript
- **Game Engine**: p5.js + p5play
- **AI/ML**: ML5.js (MoveNet for pose detection, HandPose for hand tracking)
- **Hardware**: Makey Makey
- **Libraries**: 
  - Body pose detection
  - Hand pose detection
  - Physics engine (p5play)

## ğŸ® How to Play

1. **Position yourself** in front of your webcam
2. **Do squats** to load ammunition (each squat = 1 bullet)
3. **Aim** by placing your hand in front of the webcam
4. **Shoot** using the modeling clay connected to Makey Makey
5. **Eliminate** all unhealthy food items to progress
6. **Avoid** hitting healthy food items (you'll lose a life!)
7. You have **3 lives** to complete the levels

